It sounds like you're seeking a powerful prayer for deliverance and repentance. Here's a prayer you can use:

---

Heavenly Father, I come before you today to renounce and repent of the sins of rebellion and witchcraft. I repent and renounce all sexual sins I have been involved in. I loose myself from worldliness and the desire to live and think worldly. I bind and cast out sexual immorality from my life. I repent of living a hypocritical life and chasing after the things that you hate, pursuing the things that Satan approves of. I bind all evil imaginations from my mind. I loose myself from all acts of fornication, adultery, harlotry, pornography, masturbation, and homosexual tendencies. 

In the name of Jesus Christ, I ask for your forgiveness and cleansing. Fill me with your Holy Spirit and guide me in living a life that is pleasing to you. Thank you for your grace and mercy. Amen.

---

Feel free to use this prayer as you seek healing and freedom. If you need further support or resources, let me know!
